title: Las Vegas Motor Speedway adding SAFER barriers, fan enhancements
text:
Published By: Fox Sports: Motor - Today 
When NASCAR returns to Las Vegas Motor Speedway in 2016, the 1.5-mile track will have more SAFER barriers and fan enhancements than before....
